# 接口名称: 获取行情分类
# 来源文档: spider_process.md
# 说明: 查询行情榜单分类配置，如鲸探50、禁出195、新品等。

@baseUrl = https://api.x-metash.cn

### 获取行情分类
POST {{baseUrl}}/h5/market/topList
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 示例响应
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "msg": "成功",
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": 3,
#       "name": "鲸探50",
#       "code": "759475",
#       "sort": 1,
#       "showType": 1,
#       "status": true,
#       "archiveType": 2,
#       "isOpenImpactFraction": false
#     }
#   ]
# }
